results.name: Convolution of A000010 with itself.
link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
formula: Sum_{k=1..n} phi(k)*phi(n+1-k), where phi is Euler totient function (A000010).
program: (PARI) { for (n=1, 1000, a=sum(k=1, n, eulerphi(k)*eulerphi(n+1-k)); write("b065093.txt", n, " ", a) ) } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Oct 06 2009
results.author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Nov 11 2001
